OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F388A1781777898
OL,3,CLeisure firm fined #60,000 after
OL,4,Cfootballer fatally electrocuted by
OL,5,Cfloodlight
OL,7,FA leisure company has been fined
OL,8,F#60,000 after a footballer was fatally
OL,9,Felectrocuted by a floodlight in
OL,10,FPortsmouth.
OL,12,FIn 2016, Albert Xhediku was playing
OL,13,Ffive-a-side football with friends at
OL,14,FMountbatten Leisure Centre.
OL,16,FWhen he climbed a fence to retrieve a
OL,17,Fball, he was electrocuted by a
OL,18,Ffloodlight.
OL,20,FThe 34-year-old later died in hospital.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/4
