OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,389,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38804
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F388A1781777898
OL,3,CLeisure firm fined #60,000 after
OL,4,Cfootballer fatally electrocuted by
OL,5,Cfloodlight
OL,7,F"This case is a stark reminder that
OL,8,Feffective systems must be put in place
OL,9,Fto properly assess and manage the
OL,10,Frisks posed by ageing infrastructure
OL,11,Fon their sites.
OL,13,F"As always, our thoughts remain with
OL,14,FAlbert's family and friends and we
OL,15,Fhope the conclusion of this case can
OL,16,Foffer them some comfort."
OL,26,@oD@AOUuD@AOUxD@YO]
